<br>
<br>
  <p class="titletext small">
    AR has also pops up in other technology like in modern cars. Most cars produced nowadays have guidance systems that help with driving reverse. These cars have a camera in the back of said car which overlays the path the car is currently heading with how much you're going to turn calculated. Freeing people of accidentally making a error on how much to turn or hit something due to the lack of being able to see said object.
</p>
